title: Subpanel VII: The Moral Framework of National Purpose
display_string: Subpanel VII: The Moral Framework of National Purpose, 1956-1964

subnotes.content: The files in this subseries are arranged into several sections: Organization, Membership, Papers, Meetings, and Reports. The Membership section is arranged alphabetically by the last name of the member. The Papers section and accompanying correspondence are arranged by arbitrarily-assigned paper numbers. The Meetings section and the Reports section are both arranged chronologically.

This subseries contains correspondence, memoranda, papers, drafts, and final reports. Organization files, which are brief, concern the planning of subpanel activities. Membership files, as well as the correspondence that accompanies files in the Papers section, document discussions and writing on issues considered by the subpanel. The Papers files provide comprehensive presentations of the views of various subpanel experts on selected topics. Meeting files contain summaries and sometimes minute of subpanel discussions of issues. The Reports files, containing several drafts of each report, show the progressive synthesizing of the views of a subpanel's members.
